多病态又自虐的狮子 
What a sick, masochistic lion.

826
00:57:30,512 --> 00:57:35,017
首先，爱德华是个吸血鬼 
First, Edward was a vampire.

830
00:57:53,367 --> 00:57:54,597
第三 我已经毫无保留地，无可救药地爱上了他 
And third,I was unconditionally and irrevocably in love with him.

