她只是与我的家人玩棒球 
She's just gonna play baseball with my family.

1097
01:18:25,803 --> 01:18:26,730
棒球？ 
Baseball?

1098
01:18:26,731 --> 01:18:28,824
是的，长官，这是预订的行程 
Yes sir, that's the plan.

1099
01:18:28,829 --> 01:18:30,603
贝拉要玩棒球 ? 
Bella's gonna play baseball?

1100
01:18:32,407 --> 01:18:34,348
好吧，祝你好运了 
Well, good luck with that.

1101
01:18:34,349 --> 01:18:35,362
我会照顾她的，我保证 
I'll take good care of her, I promise.

1102
01:18:42,073 --> 01:18:43,913
你还拿着我给你的防狼喷雾剂吧？ 
You still got that pepper spray?

1103
01:18:44,250 --> 01:18:45,621
是的，爸爸 
Yeah, dad.

1104
