You can take their place.

1158
01:23:27,526 --> 01:23:29,283
你们先投吧 
You go first.

1159
01:23:29,618 --> 01:23:32,294
我是个擅长投诡异曲球的人 
I'm the one with the wicked curve-ball.

1160
01:23:32,362 --> 01:23:34,667
