01:25:59,229 --> 01:26:01,027
贝拉，怎么回事 ? 
Bella, what's going on?

1200
01:26:02,078 --> 01:26:03,370
我要离开这里 
I just gotta get out of here.

1201
01:26:03,371 --> 01:26:04,631
现在就走！ 
I'm leaving..Now!

1202
01:26:11,304 --> 01:26:12,171
贝拉 ? 
Bella?

1203
01:26:13,208 --> 01:26:14,944
我要怎么对他说 ? 
What am I gonna say to him?

1204
01:26:15,362 --> 01:26:16,859
我不能伤害他 
I can't hurt him.

1205
01:26:17,562 --> 01:26:18,657
贝拉，发生什么事了 ? 
Bella, what's going on?

1206
01:26:18,658 --> 01:26:19,789
你必须这么做 
You'll just have to.

1207
01:26:21,077 --> 01:26:22,359
我在卡车里等你 
I'll be down at the truck.

1208
01:26:28,457 --> 01:26:29,826
他伤害了你？ 
Did he hurt you?

1209
01:26:30,848 --> 01:26:31,581
不 
No

1210
01:26:34,231 --> 01:26:36,222
和你分手还是什么？ 
Break up with you or something?

1211
01:26:36,558 --> 01:26:38,532
不，我...是我甩了他 
No, I... I broke up with him.

1212
01:26:40,981 --> 01:26:42,691
我以为你喜欢他 
I thought you liked him.

1213
01:26:45,475 --> 01:26:47,392
对，这就是为什么我要走 
Yeah, that's just why I have to leave.

1214
01:26:47,393 --> 01:26:49,945
我不想这样，我要回家 
I don't want this, I have to go home.

1215
01:26:51,961 --> 01:26:55,052
家？你妈妈甚至不在凤凰城 
Home ? Your mom is not even in Phoenix.

1216
01:26:56,224 --> 01:26:57,785
我在路上会打给她 
I'll call her from the road.

1217
01:26:57,886 --> 01:26:59,814
你没必要现在开车回去 
You don't have to drive home right now.

1218
01:26:59,815 --> 01:27:02,035
你可以先去睡觉 
You can sleep on it.

1219
01:27:02,101 --> 01:27:04,434
如果明早你还想走，我可以带你去机场 
If you still feel like going in the morning, I'll take you to the airport.

1220
01:27:04,435 --> 01:27:07,492
不，我想开车走，这样比较有时间思考 
No, I want to drive, it will give more time to think.

1221
01:27:07,593 --> 01:27:11,274
你放心，如果我真的累了，我会找个旅馆 我保证 
If I get really tired, I'll pull into a motel.I promise.

1222
01:27:11,275 --> 01:27:13,896
呃，贝拉，我知道跟我相处很无趣 
Look, Bella.I know I'm not that much fun to be around.

1223
01:27:13,897 --> 01:27:16,265
但是我可以改的 
But I can change that.

1224
01:27:16,803 --> 01:27:19,030
我们可以一起做很多事情的 
We can do more stuff together.

1225
01:27:21,568 --> 01:27:25,079
例如？整天盯着电视看棒球比赛？ 
Like what ? Like watch baseball on the flatscreen?

1226
01:27:26,003 --> 01:27:27,992
每晚一起吃晚饭？牛排和馅饼？ 
Eat at the dinner every night?Steak and Cobbler?

1228
01:27:34,408 --> 01:27:37,708
贝拉，别这样，我只是...想让你留下 
Bella, come on. I just... got you back.

1229
01:27:41,337 --> 01:27:43,148
是啊，你知道...如果我现在不走 我就会像妈一样永远陷在这里
Yeah, you know... If I don't get out now,I'm just gonna be just stuck here like mom.

1231
01:28:11,481 --> 01:28:13,381
你爸爸会原谅你的 
Your father's gonna forgive you.

1232
01:28:15,022 --> 01:28:16,958
让我来开吧 ? 
Why don't you let me drive?

1233
01:28:22,721 --> 01:28:24,081
他不会的 
He won't.

1234
01:28:25,313 --> 01:28:27,181
你没看到他的表情 
You should have seen his face.

1237
01:28:32,683 --> 01:28:35,281
那是唯一能让你走的方法 
It was the only way he'd let you go.

1238
01:28:37,663 --> 01:28:40,479
现在先别担心他了，他很安全 
Just don't worry about him now.He's safe.

1239
01:28:40,489 --> 01:28:41,709
追踪者正在跟着我们 
The tracker's following us.

1240
01:28:46,172 --> 01:28:47,201
那是艾密特 
It's just Emmett.

1241
01:28:49,515 --> 01:28:51,350
艾莉丝的车跟在后面 
Alice is in the car behind us.

1242
01:29:13,785 --> 01:29:14,710
等一下 ! 
Wait!

1243
01:29:15,620 --> 01:29:18,563
他是来警告我们关于詹姆斯的事 
He came to warn us About James.

1244
01:29:18,784 --> 01:29:19,995
这不是我引起的战争 
This isn't my fight

1245
01:29:19,996 --> 01:29:22,563
而且我早已厌倦他的游戏了 
And I've grown tired of his games.

1246
01:29:22,773 --> 01:29:25,579
但他拥有空前的感官能力，绝对是致命性的 
But he's got unparalleled senses, absolutely lethal.

1247
01:29:25,580 --> 01:29:28,356
三百年来，我从没见过像他那么厉害的 
I've never seen anything like him in my three hundred years.

1248
01:29:28,643 --> 01:29:32,723
还有那个女的，维多莉亚...绝不要低估了她 
And the woman, Victoria...Don't underestimate her.

1249
01:29:37,534 --> 01:29:39,788
我以前被迫与同类作战过，很难杀的死对方 
I've had to fight our kind before.We're not easy to kill.

1250
01:29:39,789 --> 01:29:40,931
但并不是不可能 
But not impossible.

1251
01:29:42,058 --> 01:29:44,174
我们会把他撕成一片片然后烧了 
We'll rip him apart and burn the pieces.

1252
01:29:44,275 --> 01:29:46,366
我并不喜好杀死另一种同类 
I don't relish the thought of killing another creature.

1254
01:29:48,862 --> 01:29:50,809
要是他先杀了我们其中一个呢？ 
What if he kills one of us first?

1255
01:29:50,810 --> 01:29:53,566
我会带贝拉逃到南方，把追踪者引开这里 
I'm gonna run Bella south and then lead the tracker away from here.

1256
01:29:53,567 --> 01:29:55,816
不，爱德华，詹姆斯知道你不可能离开贝拉 
No, Edward. James knows you'd never leave Bella.

1257
01:29:55,817 --> 01:29:56,846
他会跟踪你的 
He'll follow you.

1258
01:29:56,864 --> 01:29:59,784
我和贝拉一起走，贾斯柏和我开车带她南下 
I'll go with Bella.Jasper and I will drive her south.

1259
01:29:59,809 --> 01:30:01,474
我会保护她的，爱德华 
I'll keep her safe, Edward.

1260
01:30:01,545 --> 01:30:03,237
你们控制得住自己吗 ? 
Can you keep your thoughts to yourself?

1261
01:30:03,238 --> 01:30:04,134
是的 
Yes.

1262
01:30:08,051 --> 01:30:10,566
罗丝莉...艾丝蜜 
Rosalie... Esme.

1265
01:30:17,140 --> 01:30:19,555
为什么？她和我是什么关系？ 
Why? What is she to me?

1266
01:30:19,777 --> 01:30:21,035
罗丝莉 
Rosalie.

1267
01:30:21,177 --> 01:30:23,235
贝拉与爱德华现在是情侣 
Bella is with Edward.

1268
01:30:23,277 --> 01:30:25,235
她现在是我们家族的一份子 
She is part of this family now.

1269
01:30:26,652 --> 01:30:28,876
而我们永远会保护家人 
And we protect our family.

1270
01:30:47,860 --> 01:30:52,097
如果发生了什么意外，我发誓... 
If anything happens, I swear to God...

1271
01:30:52,098 --> 01:30:53,240
不会有事的 
Nothing's gonna happen.

1272
01:30:53,297 --> 01:30:55,840
我们是七个对付他们两个呢 
There's seven of us against two of them.

1273
01:30:55,843 --> 01:30:57,262
而且等事情结束后 我就会去接你的 
And when everything's done I'm gonna come back and get you.

1275
01:31:00,791 --> 01:31:01,765
好的 
Yeah.

1276
01:31:02,655 --> 01:31:05,276
贝拉，从现在起你就是我的生命了 
Bella, you are my life now.

1277
01:31:22,360 --> 01:31:24,198
嘿，妈妈，又是我 
Hey, mom. It's me again.

1279
01:31:26,489 --> 01:31:30,904
我现在不在福克斯，但我没事，过后再跟你解释 
I'm not in Forks but everything's okay and I'll explain it later.

1280
01:31:37,717 --> 01:31:39,975
罗丝，在树群中作标记 
Rose, among the three.

1281
01:31:41,885 --> 01:31:43,314
很好 
That's good.

1282
01:32:30,814 --> 01:32:32,807
怎么了 ? 你看见什么 ? 
What is it? What did you see?

1283
01:32:44,524 --> 01:32:46,295
被他识破了 
He figured it out.

1284
01:32:46,296 --> 01:32:49,413
追踪者，他改变路线了 
The tracker. He just changed course.

1285
01:32:51,084 --> 01:32:52,246
他往哪个方向了，艾莉丝 ? 
Where will it take him, Alice?

1286
01:32:52,247 --> 01:32:54,458
镜子...一个全是镜子的房间 
Mirrors...A room full of mirrors.

1287
01:32:59,046 --> 01:33:01,297
艾德华说你看到的不一定是正确的 
Edward said the visions weren't always certain.

1288
01:33:01,398 --> 01:33:04,780
她看到的过程必须是那个人刚好在那里 
She sees the course people are on while they're on it.

1289
01:33:04,781 --> 01:33:06,674
如果他们改变主意了，看到的也会变 
If they change their minds, the vision changes.

1290
01:33:06,675 --> 01:33:09,374
那么，追踪者现在的路线... 
So, the course that the tracker's on now is gonna...

1292
01:33:12,480 --> 01:33:13,731
你去过？ 
You've been here?

1293
01:33:13,732 --> 01:33:16,080
我小时候在那上过课 
I took lessons as a kid.

1294
01:33:16,355 --> 01:33:18,291
我去的学校有个这样的拱门 
The school I went to had an arch just like that.

1295
01:33:18,292 --> 01:33:19,490
你的学校也在凤凰城 ? 
Was your school here in Phoenix?

1296
01:33:19,491 --> 01:33:20,830
是的 
Yeah.

1297
01:33:22,452 --> 01:33:23,271
艾德华，你没事吧 ? 
Edward, you okay?

1299
01:33:25,897 --> 01:33:28,842
罗丝莉和艾丝蜜回到福克斯去保护你爸爸 
Rosalie and Esme have gone back to Forks to protect your father.

1300
01:33:28,843 --> 01:33:30,006
我马上过去找你 
I'm coming to get you.

1301
01:33:30,007 --> 01:33:33,290
然后我们一起去别的地方.
Then you and I are gonna go somewhere.

1303
01:33:34,800 --> 01:33:36,398
其它人会继续追捕他 
And the others will keep hunting.

1304
01:33:36,399 --> 01:33:39,544
我会不惜一切代价保护你的安全 
I'll do whatever it takes to make you safe.

1305
01:33:51,234 --> 01:33:53,675
嘿，妈！我很高兴你收到我的信息了 
Hey, mom! I'm glad you got my message.

1306
01:33:53,676 --> 01:33:55,143
你在家做什么？ 
What are you doing home?

1307
01:33:55,144 --> 01:33:57,985
贝拉 ! 贝拉! 贝拉 ? 你在哪儿 ? 
Bella! Bella! Bella? Where are you?

1308
01:33:58,619 --> 01:34:00,422
冷静点，没事的 
Calm down, everything's fine.

1309
01:34:00,562 --> 01:34:01,462
贝拉 ! 
Bella!

1310
01:34:01,911 --> 01:34:05,363
我晚点再跟你解释...妈，你还好吗 ? 
I'll explain everything later...Mom, are you alright?

1313
01:34:09,720 --> 01:34:11,791
让维多利亚很简单的就找到了你以前的地址 
It was just too easy for Victoria to find your previous address.

1315
01:34:13,542 --> 01:34:15,905
你住过的房子还不错 
It's a nice house you have here.

1316
01:34:15,906 --> 01:34:18,260
我本来就打算好在这等你来的 
I was prepared to wait for you.

1317
01:34:18,261 --> 01:34:20,864
但是当你妈妈接到一通你爸焦急的电话后就回家来了 
But then mom came home after she received a very worried call from your dad.

1319
01:34:23,142 --> 01:34:26,047
一切都进展的相当顺利 
It all worked out quite well.

1320
01:34:27,185 --> 01:34:28,164
等等 
Wait

1322
01:34:29,340 --> 01:34:31,382
你还有机会救她的 
You can still save her.

1323
01:34:31,894 --> 01:34:34,343
但是你必须离开你的朋友们 
But you're gonna have to get away from your friends.

1324
01:34:34,344 --> 01:34:35,765
你能做到吗？ 
Can you handle that?

1325
01:34:36,246 --> 01:34:37,544
我去哪里见你 ? 
Where should I meet you?

1326
01:34:39,796 --> 01:34:42,081
你以前的芭蕾教室如何 ? 
How about your old ballet studio?

1329
01:35:07,688 --> 01:35:09,978
我从来都没想过我会怎么死 
I'd never given much thought to how I would die

1330
01:35:11,940 --> 01:35:14,087
但为自己所爱的人而死似乎是个不错的选择 
But dying in the place of someone I love seems like a good way to go.

1332
01:35:24,135 --> 01:35:26,274
我不会因为这个让我自己面对死亡的决定而感到后悔  
I can't bring myself to regret the decisions that brought me face to face with dead.

1336
01:36:03,362 --> 01:36:04,562
妈妈 
Mom

1337
01:36:04,563 --> 01:36:05,662
贝拉?  妈！  
Bella?  Mom!

1338
01:36:05,663 --> 01:36:07,729
你在这里做什么 ? 
What are you doing in here?

1339
01:36:07,730 --> 01:36:09,310
每个人都取笑我 
Everyone makes fun of me.

1340
01:36:10,662 --> 01:36:12,953
你是个很棒的舞者 
You are a wonderful dancer.

1341
01:36:13,154 --> 01:36:15,756
妈妈，我糟透了 
Mom, I suck!

1342
01:36:16,262 --> 01:36:19,262
你一点都不糟糕 
You do not suck.

1343
01:36:28,362 --> 01:36:30,322
这段是我最喜欢的部分 
That's my favorite part.

1344
01:36:31,225 --> 01:36:33,618
你是个固执的孩子，不是吗？ 
You were a stubborn child, weren't you?

1345
01:36:35,817 --> 01:36:37,521
她根本不在这里 
She's not even here

1347
01:36:45,723 --> 01:36:49,468
所以...为了有更多的娱乐效果 我们来拍一点我们在一起的影片
so... To make things more entertaining,we are gonna make a little film of our time together.

1349
01:36:54,051 --> 01:36:57,390
我从你家里带来这个，希望你别介意 
I borrowed this from your house.I hope you don't mind.

1350
01:36:57,719 --> 01:36:58,432
好的... 
Okay...

1351
01:36:58,656 --> 01:37:03,218
然后 ....开始 ! 
And...Action!

1352
01:37:05,378 --> 01:37:07,148
这会让艾德华心碎的 
That will break Edward's little heart.

1353
01:37:08,262 --> 01:37:09,996
艾德华跟这事无关 ! 
Edward has nothing to do with this!

1355
01:37:12,189 --> 01:37:16,256
他的愤怒会让这场游戏更加有趣.
His rage will leave for more interesting sporthings.

1357
01:37:19,404 --> 01:37:21,241
我们继续吧 
And let's continue.

1358
01:37:36,420 --> 01:37:40,730
真美...非常有视觉动感 
Beautiful... Very visually dynamic.

1359
01:37:42,613 --> 01:37:44,853
我真是选对了舞台 
I chose my stage well.

1360
01:37:50,029 --> 01:37:52,769
他没勇气改造你真是太糟糕了 
It's too bad he didn't have the strength to turn you.

1362
01:37:56,804 --> 01:37:58,255
这可真是残忍 
It's cruel, really.

1363
01:38:03,103 --> 01:38:04,987
跟他说为你报仇吧 
Tell him to avenge you.

1364
01:38:05,999 --> 01:38:07,781
告诉他为你报仇！说！ 
Tell him to avenge you! Tell him!

1365
01:38:07,782 --> 01:38:08,730
艾德华，不要 ! 
Edward, don't!

1366
01:38:09,262 --> 01:38:09,962
告诉他！ 
Tell him!

1367
01:38:23,202 --> 01:38:26,683
你落单了...因为你比其它人都快 
You're alone...cause you're faster than the others.

1369
01:38:31,945 --> 01:38:34,221
我强到能杀了你 
I'm strong enough to kill you.

1370
01:38:41,286 --> 01:38:42,474
很抱歉 
I'm sorry.

1371
01:39:46,059 --> 01:39:47,862
贝拉，贝拉 ! 没事了 
Bella, Bella! It's okay.

1373
01:39:49,790 --> 01:39:52,505
够了！别失去了你的本性 
Enough! Remember who you are.

1374
01:39:58,893 --> 01:40:00,784
贝拉需要你 
Bella needs you.

1375
01:40:03,067 --> 01:40:04,277
哦，天啊 
Oh God.

1376
01:40:08,151 --> 01:40:10,121
卡莱尔 ! 这血... 
Carlisle! The blood...

1377
01:40:10,122 --> 01:40:11,683
你的兄弟们会解决他的 
Your brothers will take care of it.

1378
01:40:12,342 --> 01:40:14,115
用地上的木板生火 
Start the fire with the floor boards.

1379
01:40:16,169 --> 01:40:17,100
艾莉丝 ! 
Alice!

1380
01:40:17,289 --> 01:40:18,218
艾莉丝，快 
Alice, go.

1382
01:40:30,392 --> 01:40:32,245
不，不，我的手...烧起来了! 
No, no, my hand... Is burning!

1383
01:40:33,805 --> 01:40:35,298
那是毒液的关系 
It's the venom.

1384
01:40:36,597 --> 01:40:39,135
为了不让她转化，你必须做个选择 
You have to make a choice to prevent the change happen.

1385
01:40:39,962 --> 01:40:42,514
不... 
No...

1386
01:40:42,515 --> 01:40:43,284
不！ 
No!

1387
01:40:44,730 --> 01:40:47,006
这会发生的，艾德华，我预见到了 
It's gonna happen, Edward. I've seen it.

1388
01:40:47,007 --> 01:40:48,814
不一定非要这样做 
It doesn't have to be that way.

1389
01:40:48,815 --> 01:40:50,095
她还在出血..，艾莉丝 
She's still hemorrhaging...Alice

1390
01:40:50,096 --> 01:40:51,863
把你的皮带给我当止血带 
Make me a tourniquet with your belt.

1391
01:40:51,864 --> 01:40:54,529
卡莱尔，我还有其它选择吗 ? 
Carlisle, what's my other option?

1392
01:40:55,205 --> 01:40:56,747
把它绑在我的手上 
Tie it above my hands.

1393
01:40:57,278 --> 01:40:58,985
卡莱尔 ! 
Carlisle!

1394
01:41:00,612 --> 01:41:02,219
快 
Go.

1395
01:41:06,816 --> 01:41:08,170
试着把毒液吸出来 
To try to suck the venom out.

1396
01:41:08,171 --> 01:41:09,584
你知道我可能没办法停下来的 
You know I won't be able to stop.

1397
01:41:09,585 --> 01:41:11,772
那就用你的意志力...去阻止 
Then find the will...To stop.

1398
01:41:12,536 --> 01:41:15,621
她没几分钟可活了 
She only has minutes left.

1399
01:41:18,362 --> 01:41:20,431
我不会让你离开我的，贝拉 
I can't make you go away, Bella.

1400
01:41:22,962 --> 01:41:25,129
但我会让痛苦离开你的 
But I'll make it go away.

1401
01:41:43,321 --> 01:41:44,823
艾德华，停下来 ! 
Edward, stop!

1402
01:41:44,824 --> 01:41:47,215
血已经干净了，再下去你会杀死她的 
The blood is clean, you're killing her.

1403
01:41:48,048 --> 01:41:51,154
爱德华，停下来 ! 
